        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "An error *A DB adapter was tried to retrieve, but was not configured* is thrown at *Zend\\Application\\Resource\\Multidb.php:128* when trying to fetch a database from the multidb stack.\r\n\r\nIt looks like the init() function won't execute properly, leaving the {{$this->_dbs}} variable empty.\r\n\r\nI think the problem only occurs with plugin resources, not with *normal* resources (*log* isn't executing init() either).\r\n\r\nAre there known issues with init() and autoloading?"
        },
